DOC.brief_summary: A open label two way crossover formulation and food effect study in healthy volunteers to assess the pharmacokinetics of a single dose of AZD2066 new oral solid formulation and an oral solution
DOC.brief_title: AZD 2066 Single Dose Formulation and Food Effect Study in Healthy Volunteers
DOC.criteria: Clinical normal physical findings, including BP, pulse rate >45 bpm, ECG and laboratory assessments Body Mass Index (BMI) of ≥18 to ≤30 kg/m2 and weight of ≥50 to ≤100 kg History of hypersensitivity, allergy or atopic/skin disease as judged by Investigator. History of somatic or psychiatric disease/condition, which may interfere with the objectives of the study as judged by the Investigator.
